my vim runtime

should be used without vim's default runtime
set $VIMRUNTIME to this config's path

autoload

	- plug
		simple plugin manager

	- ft
		filetype registry

	- unmap
		unmapping default key maps

tools

	- bookmark
		bookmark management & jumping

	- browser
		simple file browser & manager

	- comment
		toggle comment

	- find
		find & grep interface

	- line
		custom statusline & bufline

	- mark
		jumping through markers

	- mode
		simple mode toggling

	- mru
		mru tracker

	- pair
		autopair in insert & visual

	- scroll
		smooth scrolling

	- search
		enhanced searching & multiline editing

	- space
		start screen

	- term
		terminal utilities

	- utils
		util commands

